This repository forms part of the OMNI Geometry research program, an independent investigation of cross-frame angular structure analysis in time-stamped event datasets.

This repository specifically constitutes the deposited reproducibility snapshot for the manuscript currently submitted to Royal Society Open Science (release tag v1.0-rsos-submission). It is not the entirety of the OMNI Geometry methodology, framework, or research program.

Users of this repository or any derivative works should cite the associated publication once available, and acknowledge the original OMNI Geometry framework.

